<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="letter-n">letter <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'letə(r)/    美 /'letər/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>信：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>write</strong> a <strong>letter to</strong> sb 
给某人写信</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>answer / reply to a letter 
回信</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Your letter reached me last Monday. 
我上周一收到了你的信。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>字母：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>capital</strong> / small <strong>letter</strong>
大/小写字母</p></div></div>